---
title: Crispy-Skinned Chicken with Smashed Potatoes, Roasted Green Beans and Rosemary Pan Sauce
description: Crisping up the skin on this chicken and serving with a luscious pan sauce, chunky smashed potatoes and fresh green beans makes for an awesome winter dish that's comforting and will stick to your ribs!
